Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------------Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 存储器都被拆除了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事先把这里废弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是花了6年才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么甘心空手而归
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据资料显示 前面是住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宠物机器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是情报终端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚缇 找到宝了 我先返舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据分析的准备工作就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与第一代 第二代的机体都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔数据库中没有相关记录的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有那样的机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有没有 我可是亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清了 看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似Gundam的MS至少存在三架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽与我们的太阳炉不同 但也放出了类似GN粒子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说 你们被那些Gundam所救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些机师在通话中提到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己为Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在离开时向我们传送了这个宇宙坐标的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和我们打招呼来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我们可是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙救了刹那他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面就一切明了了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去迎接他们吧 新的Gundam机师们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学望远镜捕捉到接近中的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在主监视器上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 准备Exia的出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝 对船体进行扫描
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷窥了 被偷窥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来对我们抱有警戒心 就随他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 从接近的船体中释放出的是GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没搞错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认船内存在4台GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们是怎么搞到太阳炉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 舱口打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 尼娜 抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认从MS发出的光通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求托勒密的着舰许可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回电 同意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 解除Exia的待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让刹那到作战会议室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到着舰许可 向托勒密行进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到着舰许可 深表感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Eins的Gundam机师 约翰·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Zwei的Gundam机师 米歇尔·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne Drei的Gundam机师 尼娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 名字都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有血缘关系 是亲兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 Exia的驾驶员是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia的Gundam机师 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢乱来的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这一点 很对我的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 竟敢对我妹妹动手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹妹不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你这装酷男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被割几刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死你了 想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙谁啊 你这家伙谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 %^&$^%&
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 在这有点不方便 到房间里谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是新的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们第一次意见相符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是不得了的一群人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌那女生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 你对刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的Gundam 没听爸爸妈妈说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们拥有Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔的数据仓库里没记录那样的机体 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奉告 我们也有守秘的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳炉 不 GN Drive是从哪里入手的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很对不起 无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们为何来此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特来拜见被老式MS臭打一顿的笨拙机师们的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑呢 说笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不佳 容我先行退席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后请向维塔提交报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 要是女人的话我就不忍心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥 真无聊 我想船内各处探险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别让我生气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 关于这点请务必告知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们准备用Gundam做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你们那样 我们也是Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 要和我们联手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你们只会那些软绵无力的武力介入 所以现在轮到我们出马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面上的意思 靠不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 不完全的改造人兄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起 我替弟弟的无礼表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 向我们下达命令的人物对你们的武力介入方式存在疑问不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被解雇了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请与以往一样继续你们的作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会凭借自己的判断来进行武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的计划中是必要的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 我认为这应该根据我们之后的行动才能得到结论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Gundam交给那些家伙的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 先使用维塔验证情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔的终端单元  竟然开着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说完想说的就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个叫约翰的家伙还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候连照片都拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样让他们回去了没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上没得到那边的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们谈话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是调查了那个叫Throne的机体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告书请输入到独立的终端里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要输入到维塔里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 那个Exia的机师 叫刹那的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙有什么好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很可爱吗 尼娜一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 下次让我见到一定把他击落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任务了 有任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有了？真会使唤人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要让世界见识一下 天行者的认真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵重的情报啊 里本斯真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我遇上你真是神的恩赐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是为此 你才把我捡回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那个相遇是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我成为天行者的监视者也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会对世界做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个监视者 仅仅在注视着世界变革而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了 定期考试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快死了 还要打工什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在考前休息一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝你还真说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 考试后的假期怎么安排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想看的电影的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要回西班牙一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要参见堂兄的婚礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那就尽情地去参加吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要变心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要变心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 您真是累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取材总是扑空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗 各阵营的官方发言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损毁的MS共计87架 阵亡人数超过200
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 据战地士兵的证言 好像有新的Gundam出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是确定的情报 不过看来天行者的秘密武器出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那个士兵的所属和姓名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是从池田先生那里传出来的流言 估计是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻约他见面 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:27.44,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}UNION军 太平洋上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅交付的任务失败了 还损失了3名优秀的Flag机师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不配作队长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新Gundam的出现 完全没有预测到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 性能的差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有与Gundam同等性能的机体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag是我军的最新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达利 我们是Flag机师 要以此为豪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？有机体突入大气圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 预测的降落地点是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什… 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.85,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}UNION 美国 MSWAD基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Gundam的能量发生机关是利用的相位拓扑原理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一切就说的通了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam机体数量稀少的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及必须要等200年以上时间的原因也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个能量发生机关的制作环境是木星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120年前出现的载人木星探查计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个计划也和Gundam的开发有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的真正目的 并不是根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测室发出通告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑为Gundam的三架机体 从EW9877方向攻向本基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全MS部队…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向各基地请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉眼捕捉到未知物体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些Gundam 新机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达目标地点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 跟我对接 一口气消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输送高浓度GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 目标是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子输送完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{{\pos(1195,990)}Launcher
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 Throne Eins GN发射器 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 不愧是大哥 做起事来毫不犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了 杂鱼一大群
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 三架新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉哈姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授他… 艾夫曼教授他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍无可忍了 不可饶恕 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥啊 让我玩一小会儿吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 马上就会结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏 蹂躏 全灭去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识一下吧 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Flag的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样被打败 是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德·梅森！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 Flag…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打够了吧 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要进行下个任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam机师是很忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要毫无意义的追击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授… 霍华德…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要欺负我们多少次才肯罢休啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙袭击了美军的基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明 维塔也没有接到情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是给我们添了光彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机师吗 那些家伙真的是Gundam机师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点露易丝 带我问候你的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事情都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饯别之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沙慈太在意别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样的沙慈就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使拥有怎样的信念或理念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上消逝的仍然是人之性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日依旧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的泪水正在飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 恶意的矛尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 将Gundam否定



